submitter Stephan Buchert <scb@irfu.se>
resources SW(60),UK(20),NO(20)
notes
Optical campaign with the Spectrographic Imaging Facility at the auroral station
in Adventdalen including a new ASK (auroral structure and kinetics) instrument
deployed at the ESR site. Two experiments are to be used, interferometer and
'arc'.
